public abstract class InterfacePlotSgt<T extends SgtPlotObject<?>>
extends InterfacePlot<MguiDouble>
implements DataSourceListener
Abstract class for displaying Scientific Graphics Toolkit (SGT) plots.

The generic type T specifies the type of JPlotLayout to be displayed.
